    </ul>

    <ol> - ordered list ; type can be "A", "roman -"I",default - numbers
        <li> </li>
        <li> </li>
    <ol>

    dl - definition list
    dt - definition term
    dd -definition description

    <dl>

        <dt> HTML </dt>
        <dd> Hyper text markup language </dd>
    </dl>

